---
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Navbar />
<Layout>

<main class="placements">

<canvas id="starCanvas"></canvas>

<section class="hero">
  <button class="slider-btn prev"><</button>
  <button class="slider-btn next">></button>
<div class="slide active">
  <div class="highlight-container">
    <img class="highlight-img left-img" src="/images/homePages/introimg1.png">
    <div class="slide-text">
      <p class="scrollpagetexts-highlight">Placement Highlights</p>
    </div>
    <img class="highlight-img right-img" src="/images/homePages/introimg2.png">
  </div>
</div>
 <div class="slide">
  <div class="image-box">
  <img class="slide-img graph-img" src="/images/homePages/placements_2d_graph.png" />
</div>
     <div class="slide-text">
    <p class="scrollpagetexts-highlight">Placement Highlights</p>
    <p class="summary">
     Over the last three graduating batches, the institute has maintained a strong and reliable placement record, Graduates from these batches have secured opportunities across a range of reputed IT firms, core industry organizations, and multinational companies, maintaining consistent industry trust in the institutes talent.
thanks to well-structured placement ecosystem, supported by structured training initiatives, practical skill development, and continued collaboration with industry partners.
    </p>
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="slide">
<div class="image-box">
  <img class="slide-img" src="/images/homePages/button22img.png" />
</div>
  <div class="slide-text">
    <p class="scrollpagetexts-highlight">2020-24 Batch</p>
    <p class="summary">
     The 2020-24 batch achieved consistent placement outcomes, with students securing roles across well-established IT service providers and industry-recognized organizations, such as TCS, Infosys, Wipro, Capgemini, along with other reputed firms, offering roles .offering roles aligned with student's technical and professional skill sets. With 45 out of 46 eligible students securing placements, the overall process reflected great effort by both department and students
    </p>
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="slide">
    <div class="image-box">
  <img class="slide-img" src="/images/homePages/button23img.png" />
</div>
<div class="slide-text">
    <p class="scrollpagetexts-highlight">2021-25 Batch</p>
    <p class="summary">
     The 2021-25 batch delivered strong  placement outcomes, Students secured roles across leading IT service providers  such as TCS, Infosys, Wipro, Accenture along with several other prominent firms. With 61 out of 62 students successfully placed, the placement process highlighted effective training initiatives, improved industry alignment, and sustained collaboration with recruiting partners
    </p>
     </div>
  </div>
  <div class="slide">
  <div class="image-box">
  <img class="slide-img" src="/images/homePages/button24img.png" />
</div>
<div class="slide-text">
    <p class="scrollpagetexts-highlight">2022-26 Batch</p>
    <p class="summary">
    The 2022-26 batch recorded stable  placement outcomes,  accommodating largest student intakes in department. Students secured opportunities across leading IT service providers and established organizations such as TCS, Infosys, Accenture, Cognizant, and Deloitte, along with other reputed recruiters. With many students successfully placed, the placement process reflected great placement efforts by department and students
    </p>
       </div>
  </div>
  <div class="dots"></div>

</section>
  <section  class="years-section">
   <h2 class="year-title">Select the Year</h2>
  <div class="years">
    <button data-year="2024">2020-24</button>
    <button data-year="2025">2021-25</button>
    <button data-year="2026">2022-26</button>
  </div>
</section>
  <section class="students hidden"></section>
  <div class="modal hidden">
  <div class="modal-card">
  <button class="close">X</button>
  <img class="student-img" />
<div class="modal-info">
  <h1 class="modal-title"> </h1>
  <h2 class="name">  </h2>
  <p class="company"> </p>
</div>
</div>
  </div>

</main>

  <style is:global >

*,
*::before,
*::after {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
.slider-btn{
  position:absolute;
  top:50%;
  transform:translateY(-50%);
  background:rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  border:2px solid #ffd88a;
  color:#ffd88a;
  font-size:2rem;
  width:50px;
  height:50px;
  border-radius:50%;
  cursor:pointer;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  z-index:50; 
  transition:all 0.3s ease;
}
.slider-btn:hover{
  background:#ffd88a;
  color:black;
}
.prev{
  left:40px;
}
.next{
  right:40px;
}
.hero {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  height: clamp(28rem, 70vh, 60rem);
  background: black;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.highlight-container{
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  gap:4rem;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
}
.highlight-img{
  width: clamp(260px, 20vw, 420px);
  height: auto;
  border-radius: 10px;
  object-fit: cover;
  animation:fadeImage 18s ease forwards,floatImage 3s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes floatImage{

  0%{ transform:translateY(0px); }

  50%{ transform:translateY(-10px); }

  100%{ transform:translateY(0px); }

}
.left-img{
  transform:translateX(-20px);
   margin-left:5rem;
}
.right-img{
  transform:translateX(20px);
  margin-right:5rem;
}
@keyframes fadeImage{
  from{
    opacity:0;
    transform:translateY(30px);
  }
  to{
    opacity:1;
    transform:translateY(0);
  }
}
.slide {
  margin-top:5rem;
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.6s ease;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  z-index: 0;
}
.slide.active {
  opacity: 1;
  z-index: 1;
}
.slide-bg {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 0;
}
.hero::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(
      rgba(56,189,248,0.35) 1px,
      transparent 1px
    ),
    linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      rgba(56,189,248,0.30) 1px,
      transparent 1px
    );
  background-size: 60px 60px;
  animation: gridMove 5s linear infinite;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 1;
}
.slide:not(:has(.slide-bg))::before {
  opacity: 0.6;
}
.hero::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  height: 100px;   
  background: linear-gradient(
    to bottom,
    rgba(0,0,0,0) 0%,
    rgba(0,0,0,0.6) 50%,
    rgba(0,0,0,0.9) 80%,
    rgba(0,0,0,1) 100%
  );
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 5;
}
@keyframes gridMove {
  0% {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
  100% {
    transform: translateY(60px);
  }
}
.slide-bg img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  object-position: center;
}
.slide-bg::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
  z-index: 1;
}
.slide:not(:has(.slide-bg)) {
  flex-direction: row;
  gap: 3.5rem;
  padding: 0 4rem;
  text-align: left;
}
.image-box {
  width: min(360px, 40vw);   
  height: 360px;            
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  background: #000;
  border-radius: 1.4rem;
  overflow: hidden;
  z-index: 2;
}
.slide-img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;    
  object-position: center;
  display: block;
}
.slide-text {
  max-width: 560px;
}
.scrollpagetexts-highlight {
  font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 3.2rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: white;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.slide:first-child .scrollpagetexts-highlight{
   transform: translateY(-40px);
     margin-top:-40px;
   font-size: clamp(3rem,3vw,4rem);
}
.summary {
  font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.3vw, 1.4rem);
  line-height: 1.6;
   margin-bottom: 5rem;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
}
.dots {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 1.8rem;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.7rem;
  z-index: 10;
}
.dot {
  width: 9px;
  height: 9px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  cursor: pointer;
}
.dot.active {
  background: #ffd88a;
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px #ffd88a;
}
.students {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(
    auto-fit,
 minmax(clamp(180px, 18vw, 230px), 1fr)
  );
  gap: 2rem;
  justify-content: center;
}
.student {
  background: linear-gradient(
      rgba(2,6,23,0.35),
      rgba(2,6,23,0.35)
    ),
    url("/images/homePages/gears_enhanced.png");
     background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  border-radius: 1.8rem;
  text-align: center;
  color: white;
  cursor: pointer;
  aspect-ratio: 4 / 6;
  padding: 1.2rem 1.2rem;
  gap: 1rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: flex-start; 
    animation: 
     glowPulse 3s ease-in-out infinite,
    floatCard 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255,216,138,0.2);
}
.student h3 {
  font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 1.6vw, 1.6rem); 
    margin-top: 0.9rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  padding-top:1rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}
.years-section {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 2rem;
}
.year-title{
  display:inline-block;       
  padding:10px 40px;
  font-size: clamp(2rem,3vw,3rem);
  color:#ffd88a;
  border:2px solid #ffd88a;
  border-radius:40px;
  margin-bottom:2rem;
}
.years {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
   gap:2rem;  
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
}
.years button{
  font-size:1.1rem;
  font-weight:600;
  padding:0.9rem 2rem;
    background:linear-gradient(
    270deg,
    #ffd88a,
    #fff3c4,
    #ffd88a
  );
  background-size:300% 300%;
  animation:yearGradient 3s ease infinite;
  transition:transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
  cursor:pointer;
  border-radius:2rem;
  box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(255,216,138,0.35);
}
@keyframes yearGradient{
  0%{
    background-position:0% 50%;
  }
  50%{
    background-position:100% 50%;
  }
  100%{
    background-position:0% 50%;
  }
}
.student-thumb {
  width: 70%;        
  max-width: 170px; 
  aspect-ratio: 3 / 4; 
  object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 1.2rem;
  border: 3px solid #ffd88a; 
    filter: brightness(0.90);
}
.modal {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.75);
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  z-index: 999;
}
.modal-card {
   background:
    linear-gradient(
      rgba(2,6,23,0.4),
      rgba(2,6,23,0.25)
    ),
    url("/images/homePages/hoveringkuma.png");
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  border-radius: 1.8rem;
  overflow: hidden;
 width: min(95vw, 900px);   
  min-height: 420px;         
  padding: 3rem;
 display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:flex-start;   
  gap:3.5rem;                   
  padding:2.5rem 3rem;
  color: white;
  position: relative;
border: 2px solid #ffd88a;
  animation: modalFloat 3s ease-in-out infinite,borderPulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.modal-card::after{
  content:"";
  position:absolute;
  inset:0;
  background:rgba(0,0,0,0.30);
  border-radius:inherit;
  z-index:0;
}
.modal-card *{
  position:relative;
  z-index:1;
}
@keyframes modalFloat {
  0% {
    transform: translateY(0px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
  }
  50% {
    transform: translateY(-12px);
    box-shadow: 0 25px 55px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
  }
  100% {
    transform: translateY(0px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
  }
}
@keyframes floatCard {
  0% {
    transform: translateY(0px);
  }
  50% {
    transform: translateY(-17px);
  }
  100% {
    transform: translateY(0px);
  }
}
.image-box:has(.graph-img) {
  width: min(480px, 50vw);
}
.modal-card .close {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0.9rem;
  right: 0.9rem;
  background: none;
  border: 2px white solid;
  color: white;
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  cursor: pointer;
}
.student-img {
  width: 200px;
  aspect-ratio: 2.8 / 4;
  object-fit: cover;
 border-radius:1rem;
  filter: brightness(0.90);
   animation: borderPulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
   border: 2px solid rgba(255,216,138,0.3); 
}
@keyframes borderPulse {
  0% {
    border-color: rgba(255,216,138,0.2);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0px rgba(255,216,138,0);
  }
  50% {
    border-color: rgb(254, 248, 235);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,216,138,0.7);
  }
  100% {
    border-color: rgba(255,216,138,0.2);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0px rgba(255,216,138,0);
  }
}
@keyframes glowPulse
{
    0% {
    border-color: rgba(255,216,138,0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0px rgba(255,216,138,0);
  }
  50% {
    border-color: rgba(255,216,138,0.9);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,216,138,0.4);
  }
  100% {
    border-color: rgba(255,216,138,0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0px rgba(255,216,138,0);
  }
}
.hidden {
  display: none;
}
.modal-info{
    display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  justify-content:center;
  gap:0.3rem;
  text-align:center; 
}
.modal-info::before{
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: -10px;
  background: linear-gradient(
    to right,
    rgba(0,0,0,0.75),
    rgba(0,0,0,0.45),
    transparent
